ikaaro 0.62.9 (2012/05/27)
==========================

This is a Content Management System built on Python & itools, among
other features ikaaro provides:

 - content and document management (index&search, metadata, etc.)
 - multilingual user interfaces and content
 - high level modules: wiki, forum, tracker, etc.

Changes
-------

Now libgit2 and pygit2 are used instead of Git whenever possible. This
increases the speed of the operations concerned, like write actions.

New configuration option "auth-cookie-expires", if set the user will be
automatically logged out after the specified number of minutes.

Now emails sent by the application have the user's email address set in
the "Reply-To" field, instead of "From". This helps emails not to be
considered as spam.

Upgrade tinymce to 3.4.9


